# MCP Template Rules

- Use `@modelcontextprotocol/sdk` primitives from the template.
- Validate tool inputs with Zod.
- Register tools with `server.registerTool()` and resources with `server.registerResource()`.
- Support stdio by default and SSE when `MCP_TRANSPORT=sse`.
- Keep the template deployable to container hosting.
- Favor small, well-described tools and resources over broad catch-all handlers.
